Instead of pulling to the cactus, run Lucan to the zone and half some newb hail him until the guards go back. Zone back in and drag Lucan into the tunnles near the North Freeport zone. After a while, Lucan's hoe,- Brother Jentry will come running down. hes no big prob if you can just keep him stunned. This is the easy way of killing Lucan if you have the 50+ to do it =]<BR>
